The paper discusses phase retrieval, which is a problem commonly encountered in signal processing and imaging. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Information Theory (cs.IT), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Numerical Analysis (cs.NA), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Signal Processing (cs.SI). Among these, cs.IT and cs.CV are the most likely categories, as the paper deals with optimization-based methods for phase retrieval, which are commonly used in these fields. The other categories are also possible, as they are related to the computational and algorithmic aspects of the problem.
